GStreamer QA System
-------------------


Pre-milestone 1 README


To run:

PYTHONPATH=/full/path/to/top/directory:$PYTHONPATH bin/gst-media-test


Inline documentation
--------------------

  The source code is commented with python-style documentation.

  You can get an html version by using epydoc and the following
command:

  epydoc -o epydoc --docformat plaintext -v  gstqa

Database support
----------------

  Currently the data is stored in a sqlite file.

  WARNING WARNING WARNING : Until milestone 1 is released, the database
  schema might change without possibilities to update the previously existing
  one.
  Milestone 1 will contain updating facilities to transfer existing databases
  to the modified schemas.
